Memoverse

MemoVerse is a tool that helps you memorize Bible verses. MemoVerse has the following features:

- User customizable Bible verse profile
- "Practice mode" that lets user enter the missing words in the verse
- Keeps track of the difficulty level achieved on a verse-by-verse level
- Print the verses in Flash Cards for offline study
- Allows one to memorize an entire passage or parts of a verse
- Timer that keeps tracks how long it took to complete a given verse
- Cross-platform. Runs on Windows, Mac OSX, Linux, and UNIX
- Open sourced, and released under the MIT license

Installation

> lein deps
> lein uberjar
> java -jar memoverse-1.0.jar

